bug.author: caisq
bug.summary: Documentation: tf.io.listModels function shows up as tf.listModels on website
bug.description:
To get help from the community, check out our <denchmark-link:https://groups.google.com/a/tensorflow.org/forum/#!forum/tfjs>Google group</denchmark-link> . <denchmark-h:h4>TensorFlow.js version</denchmark-h>
0.11.2 See <denchmark-link:https://js.tensorflow.org/api/0.11.2/#copyModel>https://js.tensorflow.org/api/0.11.2/#copyModel</denchmark-link>
Under "Models / Management", the function tf.io.listModels is incorrectly listed as tf.ilstModels. Similar problem happens for tf.io.copyModel, tf.io.moveModel and tf.io.removeModel.
